STOP ON MY ACCOUNT, JANA,

05:34.367 --> 05:36.062
WE HAVE NO
SECRETS HERE.

05:36.203 --> 05:37.500
DON'T WE?

05:37.637 --> 05:40.504
NO SECRETS. IS
THAT IT, FATHER?

05:40.640 --> 05:42.768
WHY, THAT'S ALL WE
DO HAVE. SECRETS.

05:42.909 --> 05:44.468
<i>(Jana)
THAT'S HOW WE LIVE.</i>

05:44.611 --> 05:45.942
<i>BY SHUTTING
OFF THE WORLD,</i>

05:46.079 --> 05:47.547
