06:09.102 --> 06:12.072
<i>[suspense music]</i>

06:20.080 --> 06:21.548
YOU SAID YOURSELF, JANA,

06:21.681 --> 06:24.173
THAT I DESIGNED
AND BUILT TO PERFECTION,

06:24.317 --> 06:27.218
