08:06.019 --> 08:07.384
GOOD NIGHT, SIR.

08:07.520 --> 08:09.386
GOOD NIGHT, ROBERT.

08:12.325 --> 08:15.386
OH, UH, ROBERT?

08:15.528 --> 08:16.893
THERE'S NO NEED.

08:17.030 --> 08:19.965
