OF WHAT?

08:34.014 --> 08:36.414
WHY, I THINK
THAT'S QUITE OBVIOUS.

08:36.549 --> 08:37.846
SUDDENLY, INEXPLICABLY,

08:37.984 --> 08:39.884
YOUR MOTHER AND I FIND
YOU'RE UNHAPPY.

08:40.020 --> 08:41.145
YOU'RE REBELLIOUS.

08:41.287 --> 08:44.382
DO YOU THINK THAT
PLEASES US, JANA?

08:44.524 --> 08:47.858
I DON'T KNOW.

08:47.994 --> 08:50.224
I EXPLAINED TO YOU
A LONG TIME AGO

08:50.363 --> 08:52.092
WHY I DID
WHAT I DID.

08:52.232 --> 08:54.496
WHY I RETIRED
FROM THE WORLD,

08:54.634 --> 08:56.432
AND WHY I BUILT
THESE PEOPLE.

08:56.569 --> 08:58.298
[sighs]

08:58.438 --> 09:00.805
WHAT YOU'VE DONE
TO YOURSELVES

09:00.940 --> 09:02.465
IS AN ATROCITY,

09:02.609 --> 09:04.771
<i>BUT WHAT YOU'VE DONE
TO ME IS WORSE.</i>

09:04.911 --> 09:06.640
<i>YOU'VE TURNED ME
