09:12.052 --> 09:13.486
SHALL I TELL YOU

09:13.620 --> 09:15.816
WHAT ELSE I'VE
DONE FOR YOU, JANA?

09:15.955 --> 09:17.081
I'VE KEPT YOU
FROM HARM.

09:17.223 --> 09:19.089
I'VE PROTECTED YOU
AGAINST DISEASE.

09:19.225 --> 09:21.956
<i>AND INSULATION IN THIS
