OR PREJUDICE.

09:28.001 --> 09:29.958
WELL, YOU'VE
BEEN ISOLATED, YES,

09:30.103 --> 09:31.969
BUT WHAT YOU THINK
OF AS IMPRISONMENT

09:32.105 --> 09:36.406
JUST HAPPENS TO BE ASYLUM AND
SECURITY, YES, AND SURVIVAL.

09:36.543 --> 09:39.205
ASYLUM
IN A HOTHOUSE?

09:39.345 --> 09:42.280
SECURITY IN
A MAUSOLEUM?

09:42.415 --> 09:44.440
SURVIVAL AS A
VEGETABLE SURVIVES.

09:44.584 --> 09:45.779
WHAT YOU'RE BECOMING,

09:45.919 --> 09:48.081
AND WHAT YOU'RE
MAKING ME BECOME.

09:48.221 --> 09:49.814
A VEGETABLE.

09:55.061 --> 09:56.028
THANK YOU.

09:56.162 --> 09:58.790
YES, SIR.

09:58.932 --> 10:00.422
OH.

10:00.567 --> 10:02.228
NOW, MADAM.

10:06.039 --> 10:07.564
