BE ALL, MA'AM?

10:12.045 --> 10:14.070
YES. THANK YOU,
NELDA. GOOD NIGHT.

10:14.214 --> 10:15.807
<i>GOOD NIGHT, MA'AM.</i>

10:21.221 --> 10:22.382
NELDA!

10:22.522 --> 10:24.456
<i>[suspense music]</i>

10:30.630 --> 10:32.029
