TRACKS, YOU SEE?

11:22.115 --> 11:25.813
I'VE GIVEN EACH ONE OF THEM A
MEMORY OF HIS OVVN, HAVEN'T I?

11:25.952 --> 11:27.317
YES.

11:27.453 --> 11:30.184
AND ALL OF THEM CAN
RECOUNT TO YOU IN DETAIL

11:30.323 --> 11:32.155
EVERYTHING THAT'S
HAPPENED TO THEM

11:32.292 --> 11:33.885
SINCE THEIR
EARLY CHILDHOOD,

11:34.027 --> 11:35.495
AND THEY HAD
NO CHILDHOOD.

11:35.628 --> 11:38.290
<i>THEY WERE BORN JUST AS YOU
SEE THEM NOW, WEREWT THEY'?</i>

11:38.431 --> 11:39.728
YES.

11:39.866 --> 11:42.460
LOOKING THE WAY THEY DO,
ACTING THE WAY THEY DO,

11:42.602 --> 11:44.502
