HIS OWN TALENT.

11:44.637 --> 11:46.731
ONE OF THEM WAS
BUILT AS A COOK.

11:46.873 --> 11:48.705
ANOTHER WAS BUILT
AS A MAID.

11:48.841 --> 11:51.242
THE BUTLER WAS
MANUFACTURED AS A BUTLER.

11:51.377 --> 11:54.369
THE HANDYMAN KNOWS NOTHING
BUT BEING A HANDYMAN.

11:54.514 --> 11:57.745
