ME TO DISMANTLE MACHINES.

11:57.884 --> 11:58.908
YOU'RE ASKING ME

11:59.052 --> 12:01.043
TO DESTROY
THAT WHICH HAS LIFE.

12:01.187 --> 12:02.689
LIFE?

12:02.822 --> 12:06.486
THEY'RE JUST HIGHLY
COMPLICATED TOYS.

12:06.626 --> 12:08.287
FATHER, YOU'VE
TURNED THIS HOUSE

12:08.428 --> 12:10.226
